<ab facs="#facs_243_r2l4">das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>dıeſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> für vns beſant </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_243_r2l5">vnd <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> cʒurede geſacʒt ſo ſteet ir rede vngeleıch gen deinr ſchrıft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_243_r2l6">doch <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır <expan>ſou<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> mıt Jn geredt daʒ ſıe dır ſelb <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_243_r2l7">antwurt tun <expan>ſulle<ex>n</ex></expan> . Deẅht dıch aber / daʒ du <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu Jn ıcht ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_243_r2l8"><expan>ſprehe<ex>n</ex></expan> hettſt . ſo <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır dır <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>deine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>ſcheinbotte<ex>n</ex></expan> mıt <expan>deine<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
